<br>
I have a crested mistmoore sheild and gnome skin mask so far.<br>
<br>
Ragnarson <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ubatou062671.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Batou062671</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/21/01 10:23:15 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PR and MR both over 100 advice</span><hr size=1> Gnome skin armor for the poison resists.<br>
<br>
Plat Jacinth rings for the +13 magic resists. (Though this falls under the blue diamond category, but is at least a bit easier to get.)<br>
<br>
Sarnak battle shield for +10 magic resist<br>
<br>
Sparkeling Soul Necklace Ac 2, dex 5, agi 6, sv disease 5, sv poison 5, sv magic 5 <br>
<br>
Those are the ones I know of off the top of my head.  You can also go to eq.castersrealm.com and do an advanced search looking for druid equipment with at least +5 to each resist useable by druids as it came back with a large number of items when I did the search. <p>Batou Thornhill<BR>
Wanderer of the 54th Season<BR>
The Valorous<BR>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unluien.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nluien</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/21/01 3:10:09 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PR and MR both over 100 advice</span><hr size=1> Crested MM shield 10 MR 10 PR 10 DR and other stuff<br>
Shimmering White Shroud 8 PR 8 DR<br>
Bone mask of the jarsath gives some PR and DR<br>
<br>
cant think of much else right now <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/umarikavonmordo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Marika Von Mordo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/22/01 11:59:13 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PR and MR both over 100 advice</span><hr size=1> Split paw mask:              5 MR  5 PR<br>
Split paw tunic:                  10 PR<br>
Spectral Shroud:             5 MR  5 PR<br>
Leatherfoot Raiders Cap:     5 MR<br>
Collar of undead Protection:       7 PR<br>
Shimmering white Shroud:           8 PR<br>
Split paw belt:                    5 PR<br>
Gold wolfs eye bracer:       7 MR<br>
Gold wolfs eye bracer:       7 MR<br>
Platinum jacinth ring:      13 MR<br>
Platinum jacinth ring:      13 MR<br>
Teachers Syllabus:                20 PR<br>
Crested Mistmoore shield:   10 MR 10 PR<br>
<br>
Totals:                     65 MR 70 PR<br>
<br>
Granted the leather foot raiders cap is halfing only but still these should put you over your mark and none of the items are very expensive at all.<br>
<br>
Marika von Mordo<br>
Blackguard of Xegony<br>
&lt;Venator Sapentia&gt;<br>
<br>
<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unuviancaelestis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nuvian Caelestis</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://eqforge.com/forums/icons/icon48.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/22/01 8:30:19 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://home.beseen.com/internet/nuvian/images/vegeta.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PR and MR both over 100 advice</span><hr size=1> Druids can't use the Syllabus. <p><center>
<FONT SIZE = 2>
<img src="http://members.theglobe.com/aelenya/nuv_sig.jpg">
<BR>
<a href=http://ri.poweredbyevil.com/player.cfm?player=Nuvian>profile</a><BR>
</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ushweetiepah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>shweetie pah</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/25/01 8:12:30 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://envy.gtf.org/~shweetie/brak.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PR and MR both over 100 advice</span><hr size=1> This is my current gear for poison/magic encounters<br>
<br>
Slot: Item (poison/magic)<br>
<br>
ear: electrum blue diamond (11/4)<br>
ear: electrum blue diamond (11/4)<br>
Neck: Anti-poison amulet (15/0)<br>
Face: Electrum Diamond mask (10/3)<br>
Head: Tranix Crown (0/20)<br>
Finger: Velium Diamond (8/8)<br>
Finger: Velium Diamond (8/8)<br>
Arms: Hollowed Bone Bracer (0/7) (verm also 0/7)<br>
Hand: Gloves of Harmony (1/0)<br>
Wrist: Velium Blue diamond (9/9)<br>
Wrist: Velium Blue diamond (9/9)<br>
Shoulder: Obulus Death Shroud (1/1)<br>
Back: Spectral Shroud (5/5)<br>
Chest: Splitpaw Hide Tunic (10/0)<br>
Waist: Silverleaf Girdle (0/20)<br>
Legs: Carrion Beetle Legs (5/0)<br>
Feet: GEB's (0/0)<br>
Melee1: Epic (10/10)<br>
Melee2: Crested Mistmoore Shield (10/10)<br>
Range: preserved splitpaw eye (2/0)<br>
<br>
Total (125/118) - added to the base 15/25 yields 140/143 prebuffs.<br>
Not all of this is terribly easy to get, but there's a lot of room to play with.<br>
Hope this helps you get started. <p><b>Shweetie Pah</b><br>
Hierophant<br>
big sister of <b>Tiort, the level 52 fighting gnome cleric</b><br>
Mithaniel Marr</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukatlynel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Katlynel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/26/01 10:27:48 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.asianavenue.com/indiegrrl/faedrake.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PR and MR both over 100 advice</span><hr size=1> Hah.  Let's examine this for a second, we'll ignore the gems and failure rate issue and cost of jewelcraft and velium bars.<br>
<br>
Blue diamond x 4 = 3k each just for the blue diamonds = 12k (this is assuming you could even GET 4 blue diamonds)<br>
Diamond x 3 = 1k each = 3k<br>
<br>
Cost just for the gems: 15k<br>
<br>
Anti-poison amulet: Extinct<br>
Tranix crown: priceless/unobtainable, or damn close to it<br>
Silverleaf girdle: pretty much unobtainable<br>
Epic: 100+ hours of camping shyt, and luck, and ability to get VS stone.<br>
Spectral shroud: 5k+<br>
<br>
Am I jealous?  Of course.<br>
But what I'm really asking is: is there any way to get poison and magic above 100 WITHOUT spending 20k+ on resist gear AND being level 60 and having level 60 gear?  I'm pretty stumped. <p><font face="Verdana, Arial" size="2">
Katlynel Wolfcaller
<BR>Wanderer, <a href="http://www.aradani.com/warcouncil">The War Council</a>, Saryrn
</font></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ushweetiepah.showPublicProfile?language=EN>shweetie pah</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/26/01 11:49:00 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://envy.gtf.org/~shweetie/brak.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PR and MR both over 100 advice</span><hr size=1> Well, as for the gems, you can farm allizew if you are so motivated.  make friends with a high skill jeweler :) (all my friends have).<br>
<br>
anti-poison amulet is not impossible to get, just a royal pain.  You might even be able to buy one. I bought mine for 1k /shrug.<br>
<br>
spectral shroud: I think maybe I misremembered this?  not 100% sure on what I wear, but the stats are right.  Whatever I have I bought for nowhere near 5k.  more like 250.<br>
<br>
epic, and silverleaf are probably out of reach for the average person, but a tranix crown isnt.  Just raid to tranix every chance you get. <br>
<br>
I dont see that you've said your level, so I cant really comment directly to you, but all the stuff besides epic and silverleaf are obtainable by a low 50's person with 8-12 friends in game, if they are willing to put in the work/time.<br>
<br>
There's also the earing of essence which is nice, not too hard to get piece (0/10).<br>
 <p><b>Shweetie Pah</b><br>
Hierophant<br>
big sister of <b>Tiort, the level 52 fighting gnome cleric</b><br>
Mithaniel Marr</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#e6ebd7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukalinn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kalinn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/26/01 12:23:25 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://facelink.com/Kalinn?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PR and MR both over 100 advice</span><hr size=1> there are some lovely quests also that provide some nice resist gear =)<br>
-locked rum box results in a 5 svall neck piece.  can be completely soloed by a 50+ druid easy. long quest tho.<br>
-eyepatch of plunder results in 6 svall mask.  can be soloed all but killing lodizal, and its never hard to find 2 groups to come running when hes up, for great loot.<br>
-ulthork tusks quest can score some rare gems, including diamonds and blue diamonds for resist gear.  and we can all kill ulthorks if you are over 30 =P<br>
<br>
other nice resist pieces:<br>
withered leather boots, 10 RP<br>
snakespine belt, 5 RP<br>
any gnomeskin has 5-10 RP<br>
cured tizmak armors have some RM on certain pieces<br>
<br>
a lot of resist stuff is easily attainable by a 50+ person.  i highly recommend using Allakhazams character profile.  you enter all your equipment, and then can search for upgrades based upon specific stats.  its a great resource, and their database is fairly up to date.<br>
<br>
 <p>-K<br><br>
The right to do something doesn't mean that doing it is right. -William Safire
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f5e6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ukatlynel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Katlynel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#333399>(3/26/01 12:34:06 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://members.asianavenue.com/indiegrrl/faedrake.JPG WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PR and MR both over 100 advice</span><hr size=1> I'm level 52.  The issue is pretty much that I barely have time to do exp, let alone do long quests/camps/farming for resist gear that I'll use once every few weeks at best.<br>
/sigh<br>
I don't guess I have much of a choice. <p><font face="Verdana, Arial" size="2">
Katlynel Wolfcaller
<BR>Wanderer, <a href="http://www.aradani.com/warcouncil">The War Council</a>, Saryrn
</font></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showMessage?topicID=3035.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.showMessage?topicID=3042.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.emailToFriend?topicID=3030.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.threadControl?topicID=3030.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3030.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fthedruidsgrovedruidicequipment.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=3030.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub13.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thedruidsgrovegeneral">General - EQ<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm27">General - DAOC<option value="thedruidsgrovegeneralot">General - OT<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm18">FAQ & Index<option value="thedruidsgrovefrm20">Spoilers<option value="thedruidsgrovespells">Spells<option value="thedruidsgrovequests">Quests<option value="thedruidsgrovedruidicequipment">Druidic Equipment<option value="thedruidsgrovehuntingguide">Hunting Guide<